  <brief_title>Efficacy an Safety of Volinanserin on Sleep Maintenance Insomnia With a Sub-study on Stable Type II Diabetes Mellitus</brief_title>
  <acronym>SAMS</acronym>
  <official_title>Efficacy and Safety of 2mg/Day of M100907 on Sleep Maintenance Insomnia With a Sub-study of the Effect of M100907 on Stable Type II Diabetes Mellitus: a One Year, Multi-center, Randomized, Double-blind, Placebo-controlled Study</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>Sanofi</agency>
      <agency_class>Industry</agency_class>
    </lead_sponsor>
  </sponsors>
  <source>Sanofi</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to assess efficacy and safety of volinanserin in the population
      of patients complaining of sleep maintenance insomnia. The objective of the substudy is to
      assess glycemic control in the subgroup of patients with type II diabetes mellitus.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
